/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-atlas/execution/instances/quantum-gravity-2/strategies/strategy-004/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md:238:**The remnant temperature is exactly T = 0 in the extremal limit.** The remnant is thermodynamically stable — it has zero temperature and zero entropy flux.
